### Teste: API rodando
GET http://localhost:3333/

###

### Cadastrar usuário
POST http://localhost:3333/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Caua",
  "email": "caua@teste.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

###

### Login
POST http://localhost:3333/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "caua@teste.com",
  "password": "senha123"
}

###

### Tentativa de cadastro duplicado (deve dar erro)
POST http://localhost:3333/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Caua Dois",
  "email": "caua@teste.com",
  "password": "outraSenha"
}

###

### Login com senha errada (deve dar erro)
POST http://localhost:3333/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "caua@teste.com",
  "password": "senhaErrada"
}

